{
  "script_id": "brownian-motion",
  "voice": "zh-CN-YunxiNeural",
  "voice_key": "yunxi",
  "files": [
    {
      "script_id": "brownian-motion",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-1",
      "filename": "intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/brownian-motion/intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.42,
      "size": 38736,
      "text": "1827年，植物学家布朗透过显微镜，看见水中的花粉不停颤动。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "brownian-motion",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-2",
      "filename": "intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/brownian-motion/intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.94,
      "size": 31104,
      "text": "它们没有生命，却像着了魔一样，永不停歇地随机舞动。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "brownian-motion",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-3",
      "filename": "intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/brownian-motion/intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.98,
      "size": 31680,
      "text": "这背后是无数看不见的水分子，在四面八方撞击它。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "brownian-motion",
      "section_id": "increment",
      "line_id": "inc-1",
      "filename": "increment-inc-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/brownian-motion/increment-inc-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.57,
      "size": 25056,
      "text": "我们把这种运动理解成一步步的随机漫步。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "brownian-motion",
      "section_id": "increment",
      "line_id": "inc-2",
      "filename": "increment-inc-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/brownian-motion/increment-inc-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.7,
      "size": 27216,
      "text": "每一步的位移，是一个均值为零的高斯随机数。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "brownian-motion",
      "section_id": "increment",
      "line_id": "inc-3",
      "filename": "increment-inc-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/brownian-motion/increment-inc-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.9,
      "size": 30384,
      "text": "把这些独立的增量不断累加，就画出了曲折的布朗轨迹。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "brownian-motion",
      "section_id": "variance",
      "line_id": "var-1",
      "filename": "variance-var-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/brownian-motion/variance-var-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.97,
      "size": 31536,
      "text": "因为每步相互独立，位置的方差等于各步方差之和。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "brownian-motion",
      "section_id": "variance",
      "line_id": "var-2",
      "filename": "variance-var-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/brownian-motion/variance-var-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.07,
      "size": 33120,
      "text": "于是方差随时间线性增长，走得越久，散得越开。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "brownian-motion",
      "section_id": "variance",
      "line_id": "var-3",
      "filename": "variance-var-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/brownian-motion/variance-var-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.59,
      "size": 25488,
      "text": "典型的偏离距离，正比于时间的平方根。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "brownian-motion",
      "section_id": "nondiff",
      "line_id": "nd-1",
      "filename": "nondiff-nd-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/brownian-motion/nondiff-nd-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.49,
      "size": 23904,
      "text": "布朗轨迹是连续的，笔尖从不离开纸面。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "brownian-motion",
      "section_id": "nondiff",
      "line_id": "nd-2",
      "filename": "nondiff-nd-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/brownian-motion/nondiff-nd-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.24,
      "size": 35856,
      "text": "可无论放大多少倍，它依然锯齿密布，处处求不出切线的斜率。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "brownian-motion",
      "section_id": "nondiff",
      "line_id": "nd-3",
      "filename": "nondiff-nd-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/brownian-motion/nondiff-nd-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.95,
      "size": 31248,
      "text": "这就是数学中著名的：处处连续，却处处不可导。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "brownian-motion",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-1",
      "filename": "interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/brownian-motion/interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.84,
      "size": 29520,
      "text": "点击重新随机，每一次都生成一条独一无二的路径。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "brownian-motion",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-2",
      "filename": "interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/brownian-motion/interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.13,
      "size": 34128,
      "text": "在一维和二维之间切换，感受随机漫步如何铺满平面。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "brownian-motion",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-1",
      "filename": "summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/brownian-motion/summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.48,
      "size": 23616,
      "text": "布朗运动由独立的高斯增量累加而成。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "brownian-motion",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-2",
      "filename": "summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/brownian-motion/summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.15,
      "size": 34416,
      "text": "它的方差随时间线性增长，轨迹连续却处处不可导。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "brownian-motion",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-3",
      "filename": "summary-sum-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/brownian-motion/summary-sum-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.93,
      "size": 30816,
      "text": "从花粉到股价，随机之中自有规律，我们下次再见！"
    }
  ],
